          "title": "The Forgotten Song",
          "paragraphs": [
            "Orra remembers the migration song in fragments, each tied to a hive or wind wheel that no longer stands. Mara rebuilds the resonators while Iven aligns them with channels hidden inside the aqueduct stones.",
            "Years of silence gather around the final missing note as the Echo Shepherd, a spectral keeper that sends every sound back incomplete. Orra must trust Mara to carry the melody forward when her own voice falters."
          ],
