          "paragraphs": [
            "The recovered song opens passages sealed since the aqueduct's construction. Mara hears roots pressing against one wall while Iven calculates how to release each gate without collapsing the water supply above them.",
            "The original control system wakes as the Gatehouse Automaton, a clockwork warden that recognizes water pressure but not living roots. They must teach its rigid sequence a new balance before the corridor floods."
