          "id": "chapter-5-arrival",
          "title": "The Stone Barrier",
          "paragraphs": [
            "The waking forest reaches the aqueduct and stops. Iven discovers that its celebrated kiln-fired foundation lies directly across the seasonal migration route, and opening a passage will interrupt the valley's carefully controlled water.",
            "Heat trapped in the foundation rises as the Kilnstone Titan, a volcanic guardian formed from Iven's certainty that strong work must never change. He and Mara must cool, brace, and reshape the structure without pretending it can remain untouched."
          ],
          "semanticLabel": "Mara and Iven confront a glowing stone titan emerging from the baked foundations of the aqueduct.",
          "actionLabel": "Open the foundation"
        }
      ]
